*Kreten* je bio jako namršten. (The fool was very frowning.)

On je rekao da je *kreten*. (He said he was a fool.)

Bila je uvređena što je nazvali *kretenom*. (She was offended to be called a fool.)

Niko nije želeo da se druži sa *kretenom*. (Nobody wanted to hang out with the fool.)

On je uvek govorio da je *kreten*. (He was always talking about being a fool.)

Niko nije znao zašto je on postao *kreten*. (Nobody knew why he became a fool.)